everyone is divided by the next neighbour, there will be N-1 results. If the divided value is larger than 1, that means
the neighbour goes up, else the neighbour goes down. Then we can calculate the similarity of the patterns based on
the results.
The application of our research is to measure the affinity or similarity of the countries‚Äô industries. If there are N
industries in country i and the industries are labelled by 1, 2, and 3ƒÇN in turn, the industry structure of the country
can be calculated from the following formula.
